# 📝 Modern Blog Application

A fully functional and visually appealing *Blog Application* built for internship learning using:

- 🔧 *Node.js* + *Express.js* for backend
- 🔥 *Firebase Firestore* as the cloud NoSQL database
- 🌐 *HTML, CSS, JavaScript* for frontend
- 🎨 Stylish *modern UI* with Dark Mode
- ✏ CRUD features (Create, Read, Update, Delete)
- 👍 Like + 📤 Share buttons (Frontend Only)
---
link:https://blog-app-a22b1.web.app

## 🚀 Features

- ✍ Create blog posts
- 📖 View all blog posts (latest first)
- 🔄 Edit and 🗑 Delete blogs
- 🌗 Dark Mode toggle
- 👍 Like button (local count)
- 📤 Share blog (copy text or use Web Share API)
- 🎨 Clean, professional blog UI with background gradients, rounded elements, and Google Fonts

---

## 🛠 Technologies Used

| Category        | Technology                          |
|-----------------|--------------------------------------|
| *Frontend*    | HTML, CSS, JavaScript                |
| *Backend*     | Node.js, Express.js                  |
| *Database*    | Firebase Firestore (NoSQL)           |
| *Admin SDK*   | Firebase Admin SDK (for secure server access) |
| *Styling*     | CSS Flexbox, Google Fonts (Poppins), Transitions |
| *Optional*    | Firebase Hosting / Vercel (for deployment) |

